# 📊 Network Usage Tracker

A desktop-based network monitoring application built with **Python**, **Tkinter**, and **Psutil** that provides real-time network usage statistics, internet connectivity status, and bandwidth usage alerts through an intuitive graphical interface.

---

## 🚀 Overview

Network Usage Tracker is designed to monitor network activity in real time. It continuously tracks incoming and outgoing network traffic, displays current bandwidth consumption, checks internet connectivity, and notifies users when usage exceeds a predefined threshold.

This project demonstrates practical implementation of GUI development, system monitoring, networking concepts, and real-time data processing using Python.

---

## ✨ Features

* 📈 Real-time network usage monitoring
* 🌐 Internet connectivity status detection
* 🖥️ Local IP address display
* 🚨 Bandwidth threshold alert notifications
* 🎨 Modern and user-friendly GUI
* ⚡ Live updates without freezing the interface
* 🔄 Continuous network activity tracking
* 💻 Cross-platform Python implementation

