## 🔍 How It Works

1. Retrieves network I/O statistics using the **Psutil** library.
2. Calculates sent and received bytes to determine current network usage.
3. Checks internet connectivity using socket connections.
4. Displays bandwidth usage and connection status in real time.
5. Generates an alert when usage exceeds the configured threshold.

